{"tid":637823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"煙不離手既阿叔真係好佩服....","createTime":"2018-04-22T07:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T07:35:14.000Z","uid":119688,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14b23cd237ee07c581d3f9578cce8096f93873c6","tid":637823,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"自問我阿哥已經好痴線 一日兩包幾<br />\n十分鐘內必有一飛<br />\n但我琴晚約條女食煲仔飯<br />\n我對面果位阿叔真心誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我9點落去食到十點幾<br />\n見住台面個煙兜由無變到满撚左<br />\n仲要叫人換兜繼續比佢扯<br />\n因為真係太多我無數到<br />\nd人離遠以為火警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果諗落全程食餐飯<br />\n我聽到至小廿幾下火機聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8320944d2017ba07656df6b402858abf0fd34c15","tid":637823,"uid":41524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"仲好<br />\n啲廢中唔生癌死冇用"},{"pid":"e0bce1d28916af1ffde1ef143e75102aaa612ab3","tid":637823,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:34:28.000Z","msg":"祝死煙鏟<br />\n長命百歲<br />\n百病纏身"},{"pid":"5097d5a79368ee4d11f6aac1ef84c8e10ef0b90c","tid":637823,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}